            "value": "Discord は既定でオフです。TokenPilot 用に作成した Discord チャンネル Webhook だけを貼り付けてください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Webhook URL is stored in TokenPilot's own Keychain item and is never shown in plain text after saving.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ko": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Webhook URL은 TokenPilot 자체 Keychain 항목에 저장되며, 저장 후 평문으로 표시하지 않습니다."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Webhook URL is stored in TokenPilot's own Keychain item and is never shown in plain text after saving."
          }
